<h2 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 0;">Email Address Changed</h2>

<p>Hi there,</p>

<div style="background: #eff6ff; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;">
  <p style="margin: 0; color: #1e40af;">
    <% if @resource.try(:unconfirmed_email?) %>
      Your email address is being changed to <strong><%= @resource.unconfirmed_email %></strong>.
    <% else %>
      Your email address has been changed to <strong><%= @resource.email %></strong>.
    <% end %>
  </p>
</div>

<p>If you didn't make this change, please contact us immediately by replying to this email.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 24px;">
  <strong>The Acer Coffee Team</strong>
</p>
